msg":"<blockquote>所以係香港寧願得罪人都唔好得罪貓狗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\non9，咩叫唔好得罪貓狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e5309fc58399e86b6b8413408efcc006f74d70","tid":416084,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T13:58:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>所以係香港寧願得罪人都唔好得罪貓狗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\non9，咩叫唔好得罪貓狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n別再做情人 做隻貓做隻狗"},{"pid":"ba71d13476fd4373824c550e2114a00f23a67992","tid":416084,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T13:54:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">涉將小狗掟落地再腳踢　寶田邨虐狗男落網</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170927/s00001/8bae3a77912d9c3aee9eba5f7e3a51c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170927%2Fs00001%2F8bae3a77912d9c3aee9eba5f7e3a51c1.jpg&h=ff1859a4&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n近日網上流傳一段短片顯示一名穿白衫的中年男子，在屯門寶田邨一間超市收銀處位置，將一隻啡色小狗擲到地上，再起飛腳踢向小狗，將小狗趕出超市。警方昨晚拘捕一名53歲男子，涉嫌殘酷對待動物。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，近日留意到網上一段短片，顯示一名男子於9月24日在寶田商場一店舖內襲擊一頭狗。屯門警區刑事調查隊及屯門分區特遣隊人員經調查後，昨晚約11時30在寶田邨一單位拘捕一名53歲姓呂本地男子，他涉嫌殘酷對待動物，現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n案件交屯門警區刑事調查隊五隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170927/s00001/1506477646479\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170927%2Fs00001%2F1506477646479&d=WsmKV74dZ2wOEB46lhTzWwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=b76b284e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170927%2Fs00001%2F1506477646479&h=6e481e54\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170927/s00001/1506477646479</a>"}]}